```plantuml
@startuml DanNguyenN_CompassUTD

' Define components
package "CompassUTD Application" {
    [FastAPI Application] <<Microservice>>
    [Inference Engine] <<Component>>
    [Langchain Tools] <<Microservice>>
    [Web Scraping Module] <<Component>>
    [Content Filtering] <<Component>>
    [MongoDB] <<Database>>
}

' Define external services
package "External Services" {
    [Google PaLM 2] <<Service>>
    [Google Cloud Run] <<Cloud Service>>
}

' Relationships and deployment focus
[FastAPI Application] -> [Inference Engine] : Handles requests
[Inference Engine] -> [Langchain Tools] : Orchestrates logic
[Langchain Tools] -> [Web Scraping Module] : Retrieves data
[Inference Engine] -> [Content Filtering] : Filters user input
[FastAPI Application] -> [MongoDB] : Stores chat history
[Inference Engine] -> [Google PaLM 2] : Performs NLP tasks

' Deployment on cloud
[FastAPI Application] --> [Google Cloud Run] : Deploys on
[Inference Engine] --> [Google Cloud Run] : Deploys on
[Langchain Tools] --> [Google Cloud Run] : Deploys on
[Web Scraping Module] --> [Google Cloud Run] : Deploys on
[Content Filtering] --> [Google Cloud Run] : Deploys on

' Notes for deployment
note right of [Google Cloud Run]
  CompassUTD is deployed
  using Google Cloud Run
  for scalability and
  efficient resource management.
end note

@enduml
```
